data.description: Welcome Home to your Meticulously Maintained 2 Bed, One and a Half Bath Townhouse with 2 Car Garage. As you Enter you will Notice the 9' Ceilings and the Open Floor Plan. Entertain Family and  Friends in your Spacious Kitchen which Leads into the Dining Room with Balcony, a Perfect Place to Grill or Enjoy your Morning Coffee. Relax in your Owners Suite with Vaulted Ceilings, a Spacious Walk-In Closet and Private Entrance to the Full Bathroom. The 2nd Bedroom is Spacious with Ample Closet Space. Enjoy the Convenience of your 2nd Floor Laundry. All appliances are 5 Years or Newer with a Brand New AC and Water Heater from 2020. Close to Highways, Shopping, Dining and Parks. Plainfield 202 Schools!!! Don't Miss this Gem.
